CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B7, reads: "Electrical Engineering student Adolphus Patterson, of 7632 Forest Wy., received his Bachelor of Science Degree at Tech"
TitMainTitle: Men wearing dark caps and gowns, including Adolphus Patterson also wearing eyeglasses, recipient of Bachelor of Science Degree, at Carnegie Institute of Technology [Carnegie Mellon University] graduation
